---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Disclaimer from '../../components/Disclaimer.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const post = {
  title: "Paper Trading Phase Started",
  date: "2026-06-20",
  tag: "Milestone",
  tagColor: "text-accent-400",
  summary: "SPA officially entered paper trading with $100,000 USDC virtual capital across 20 DeFi adapters on Ethereum and Base.",
};
---

<Layout
  title="Paper Trading Phase Started — SPA Blog"
  description="SPA officially entered paper trading with $100,000 USDC virtual capital across 20 DeFi adapters on Ethereum and Base."
  canonical="https://earn-defi.com/blog/2026-06-20-paper-trading-started"
>

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-5 border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7" aria-hidden="true" />
        <span class="font-semibold text-white tracking-tight">SPA</span>
      </a>
      <span class="text-white/15 mx-2">/</span>
      <a href="/blog" class="text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors">Blog</a>
      <span class="text-white/15 mx-2">/</span>
      <span class="text-sm text-white/30 hidden sm:inline">Paper Trading Phase Started</span>
    </div>
    <a
      href="/dashboard"
      class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md border border-accent-500/50 text-accent-400 text-xs font-medium hover:border-accent-400 hover:text-accent-300 transition-all"
    >
      Dashboard ↗
    </a>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Header -->
    <section class="pt-16 pb-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class={`text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider ${post.tagColor}`}>{post.tag}</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-white/25 font-mono">{post.date}</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">
        {post.title}
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-lg leading-relaxed">{post.summary}</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Body -->
    <article class="pb-16 space-y-8 text-white/60 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <p>
          After completing our Backtest Gate and Pre-Paper Gate validations, SPA has officially entered the
          <strong class="text-white">Paper Trading Phase</strong> as of June 10, 2026.
          All cycles now run with <code class="font-mono text-accent-400 text-sm bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">is_demo: false</code> —
          meaning every trade, rebalance, and yield accrual is part of the official 30-day evidence track.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Gate checklist -->
      <section>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-4">Gate Status</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          {[
            { label: 'Backtest Gate',   status: 'PASS', color: 'text-green-400' },
            { label: 'Pre-Paper Gate',  status: 'PASS', color: 'text-green-400' },
            { label: 'Paper Trading',   status: 'IN PROGRESS', color: 'text-accent-400' },
            { label: 'Live Capital',    status: 'LOCKED',  color: 'text-white/30' },
          ].map(g => (
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/8">
              <span class="text-sm text-white/60">{g.label}</span>
              <span class={`text-xs font-mono ${g.color}`}>{g.status}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What this means -->
      <section>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-4">What Paper Trading Means</p>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <p>
            Paper trading runs the full production cycle — adapter scans, RiskPolicy gates, strategy tournament,
            and StrategyAllocator rebalancing — against live DeFi data. The only difference from live trading
            is that no real capital moves on-chain.
          </p>
          <p>
            Each clean daily cycle contributes <strong class="text-white">1.0 evidence point</strong> toward
            the 30-point threshold required for GoLiveChecker to reach READY status.
            Cycles during extreme-market conditions score 1.5 points.
          </p>
          <p>
            The GoLiveChecker evaluates 26 criteria. Current status: <strong class="text-white">16/26 pass</strong>.
            Target go-live: <strong class="text-white">August 1, 2026</strong> (ADR-002).
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Adapters -->
      <section>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-4">Active Adapters</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {[
            'Aave V3 (ETH)', 'Aave V3 (Arbitrum)', 'Compound V3', 'Morpho Blue',
            'Morpho Steakhouse', 'Yearn V3', 'Euler V2', 'Maple',
            'Pendle PT', 'Sky/sUSDS',
          ].map(a => (
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] text-white/45 font-mono text-xs">
              {a}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What's next -->
      <section>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-4">What's Next</p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          {[
            'Accumulate 30 clean daily evidence cycles (ETA: ~July 10, 2026)',
            'Reach 26/26 GoLiveChecker criteria',
            'gap_monitor: 30 consecutive days without gaps',
            'Owner manual review + ADR-002 sign-off',
            'Go-live: estimated August 1, 2026',
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5">
              <span class="text-accent-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">›</span>
              <span class="text-white/50">{item}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

    </article>

    <!-- Nav between posts -->
    <div class="py-8 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/blog" class="text-sm text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors">← All posts</a>
      <a href="/blog/2026-06-19-architecture-audit" class="text-sm text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        Architecture Audit →
      </a>
    </div>

  </main>

  <Disclaimer />
  <Footer />

</Layout>
